reviewText: I was extremely happy with my order
Haven't  seen a child, that doesn't  just love these. Bought this for my grt. Grandson Caden at 3 months. He loves it!
A very good dvd for kids and family who would like to get basic signing skills.
We are watching it right now, September 6th.  Ha ha.  My two year old daughter loves all the Baby Einsteins, but this is one of her favs.
